title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 26 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 26 2021
description:
WSJ: Four U.S. Marines killed in Afghanistan. South Dakota Governor Kristi Noem: Responsibility for disaster in Afghanistan lies solely with Joe Biden. Buck challenges Noem on opposition to bills on vaccine mandates and transgender sports. Fallout and reaction to Buck's spirited discussion with Governor Noem. Our freedom is on the line, it's time for Republicans to use all power at our disposal to save it.
